---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Contact-sheet review"
permalink: "/review/"
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
---

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Contact-sheet review</h1>
    <p class="lede">Click any photo to mark it for cut. Selections persist across pages in your browser. When you're done, export <code>cuts.json</code> and run <code>npm run apply-cuts</code>.</p>
    <p style="background:#fff3cd; border-left:4px solid var(--color-rope); padding:0.75rem 1rem; margin-top:1.5rem; border-radius:4px;">
      <strong>Dev-only.</strong> This page is excluded from production builds. It only appears when you run <code>npm run review</code>.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="page-body">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Tools</h2>
    <ul style="list-style:none; padding:0; margin:0 0 2rem;">
      <li style="background:#fff; border:1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius:var(--radius); padding:1rem 1.25rem; margin-bottom:0.75rem;">
        <strong><a href="/review/similar/">Similar-image review</a></strong> &mdash;
        groups of perceptually-similar photos found across the gallery.
        Generate with <code>npm run find-similar</code>; refresh this page after.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Categories</h2>
    <ul class="card-grid">
      {% for cat in gallery.categories %}
        <li class="card">
          <a href="/review/{{ cat.area }}/{{ cat.slug }}/">
            <div class="card-thumb">
              {% if cat.thumb %}
                {% responsiveImage cat.thumb, cat.title, "(min-width: 1000px) 33vw, (min-width: 600px) 50vw, 100vw" %}
              {% endif %}
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
              <h3>{{ cat.areaTitle }} &raquo; {{ cat.title }}</h3>
              <p class="count">{{ cat.imageCount }} photo{% if cat.imageCount != 1 %}s{% endif %}</p>
            </div>
          </a>
        </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>
